<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Appointment Rescheduled - TechTrainers</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe
      UI', Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #292524; margin: 0;
      padding: 0; background-color: #fafaf9; } .container { max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; overflow:
      hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); } .header { background:
      linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b 0%, #d97706 100%); color: white; padding:
      30px; text-align: center; } .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 700; } .header p { margin: 10px 0 0 0; font-size: 16px;
      opacity: 0.9; } .content { padding: 30px; } .appointment-comparison {
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin: 20px 0; gap: 20px;
      } .appointment-card { flex: 1; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; }
      .old-appointment { background: #fef2f2; border: 1px solid #fecaca; }
      .new-appointment { background: #f0fdf4; border: 1px solid #bbf7d0; }
      .appointment-card h3 { margin: 0 0 15px 0; font-size: 16px; text-align:
      center; } .old-appointment h3 { color: #dc2626; } .new-appointment h3 {
      color: #16a34a; } .appointment-detail { display: flex; justify-content:
      space-between; margin-bottom: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; border-bottom:
      1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1); } .appointment-detail:last-child {
      border-bottom: none; margin-bottom: 0; padding-bottom: 0; } .detail-label
      { font-weight: 600; color: #64748b; min-width: 80px; font-size: 14px; }
      .detail-value { color: #1e293b; font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px; }
      .trainer-info { background: #f8fafc; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; } .trainer-info h3 {
      margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #374151; font-size: 16px; } .action-buttons {
      text-align: center; margin: 30px 0; } .btn { display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 30px; margin: 0 10px; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration:
      none; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; transition: all 0.3s ease; }
      .btn-primary { background: #f59e0b; color: white; } .btn-secondary {
      background: #6b7280; color: white; } .btn:hover { transform:
      translateY(-1px); box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15); } .footer {
      background: #292524; color: #a8a29e; padding: 20px; text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px; } .footer a { color: #d97706; text-decoration: none; }
      .footer a:hover { text-decoration: underline; } .divider { height: 1px;
      background: #e2e8f0; margin: 20px 0; } .reschedule-badge { background:
      #fef3c7; color: #d97706; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 20px;
      font-weight: 500; font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px; } .calendar-attachment { background: #f1f5f9;
      border: 1px solid #cbd5e1; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px; margin: 20px
      0; text-align: center; } .arrow-indicator { text-align: center; font-size:
      24px; color: #f59e0b; margin: 10px 0; } @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .appointment-comparison { flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
      .arrow-indicator { transform: rotate(90deg); } } @media (max-width: 600px)
      { .container { margin: 0; border-radius: 0; } .content { padding: 20px; }
      .header { padding: 20px; } .btn { display: block; margin: 10px 0; } }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>üìÖ Appointment Rescheduled</h1>
        <p>Your training session has been moved to a new time</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <p>Hi <strong>{{clientName}}</strong>,</p>

        <p>Your appointment has been successfully rescheduled! We've updated
          your booking and sent you a new calendar invitation.</p>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 20px 0;">
          <span class="reschedule-badge">üìÖ Rescheduled</span>
        </div>

        <div class="appointment-comparison">
          <div class="appointment-card old-appointment">
            <h3>‚ùå Previous Appointment</h3>
            <div class="appointment-detail">
              <span class="detail-label">üìÖ Date:</span>
              <span class="detail-value">{{oldAppointmentDate}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="appointment-detail">
              <span class="detail-label">‚è∞ Time:</span>
              <span class="detail-value">{{oldAppointmentTime}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="appointment-detail">
              <span class="detail-label">üí™ Type:</span>
              <span class="detail-value">{{sessionType}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="appointment-detail">
              <span class="detail-label">üìç Location:</span>
              <span class="detail-value">{{oldLocation}}</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="appointment-card new-appointment">
            <h3>‚úÖ New Appointment</h3>
            <div class="appointment-detail">
              <span class="detail-label">üìÖ Date:</span>
              <span class="detail-value">{{newAppointmentDate}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="appointment-detail">
              <span class="detail-label">‚è∞ Time:</span>
              <span class="detail-value">{{newAppointmentTime}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="appointment-detail">
              <span class="detail-label">üí™ Type:</span>
              <span class="detail-value">{{sessionType}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="appointment-detail">
              <span class="detail-label">üìç Location:</span>
              <span class="detail-value">{{newLocation}}</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="arrow-indicator">
          ‚û°Ô∏è
        </div>

        <div class="trainer-info">
          <h3>üèãÔ∏è Your Personal Trainer</h3>
          <div class="appointment-detail">
            <span class="detail-label">Name:</span>
            <span class="detail-value">{{trainerName}}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="appointment-detail">
            <span class="detail-label">Contact:</span>
            <span class="detail-value">{{trainerEmail}}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="appointment-detail">
            <span class="detail-label">Specialization:</span>
            <span class="detail-value">{{trainerSpecialization}}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="appointment-detail">
            <span class="detail-label">Booking ID:</span>
            <span class="detail-value">{{bookingId}}</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="calendar-attachment">
          <p><strong>üìÖ Updated Calendar Invitation</strong></p>
          <p>A new calendar invitation has been sent to replace the previous
            one. Please update your calendar with the new time.</p>
          <small>The old calendar event will be automatically cancelled.</small>
        </div>

        <div class="action-buttons">
          <a href="{{viewAppointmentUrl}}" class="btn btn-primary">üì± View in
            App</a>
          <a href="{{addToCalendarUrl}}" class="btn btn-secondary">üìÖ Add to
            Calendar</a>
        </div>

        <div class="divider"></div>

        <p><strong>üìù Reschedule Details:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Rescheduled by:</strong> {{rescheduledBy}}</li>
          <li><strong>Reschedule time:</strong> {{rescheduleTime}}</li>
          {{#if rescheduleReason}}
            <li><strong>Reason:</strong> {{rescheduleReason}}</li>
          {{/if}}
          <li><strong>Duration:</strong> {{duration}} minutes</li>
        </ul>

        <p><strong>‚è∞ Important Reminders:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Please arrive 5-10 minutes early for your new appointment time</li>
          <li>Bring comfortable workout clothes, water, and a towel</li>
          <li>If you need to make any changes, please contact us at least 24
            hours in advance</li>
          <li>Your trainer will contact you if there are any specific
            preparations needed</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="divider"></div>

        <p>Thank you for your flexibility! We appreciate your understanding and
          look forward to your session at the new time.</p>

        <p>If you have any questions or need to make further changes, please
          contact us at
          <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a>
          or visit our
          <a href="{{supportUrl}}">Support Center</a>.</p>

        <p>Best regards,<br />
          <strong>The TechTrainers Team</strong></p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>
          <strong>TechTrainers</strong>
          - Empowering Fitness Through Technology<br />
          <a href="{{companyWebsite}}">{{companyWebsite}}</a>
          |
          <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a><br />
          <a href="{{manageAppointmentsUrl}}">Manage Appointments</a>
          |
          <a href="{{unsubscribeUrl}}">Unsubscribe</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>